function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	-- Vigo opens gate
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorVigo, 0.1)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorVigo)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(doorMineGate)
	
	-- Vigo and Neyrelle run to lift	
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorNeyrelle, 1.0)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorVigo, locLiftMachinery, "NPC_RUN", false)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorNeyrelle, locNeyrelleRunToOreLift, "NPC_RUN", false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorVigo, locLiftMachinery)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorNeyrelle, locNeyrelleRunToOreLift)
	
	-- Vigo tinkering anim goes here (useloop looks to be good enough)
	Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(actorVigo, animUseLoop, animUseLoop)
end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- Define followers again
	followerVigo = idActor
	followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(neyrelleFollowerSno)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		-- Neyrelle no longer a follower
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false)
		
		-- Neyrelle Travel to Convo marker loc
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(followerNeyrelle, locCSDGateUnlockNeyrelle, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_RUN, true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, locCSDGateUnlockNeyrelle)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerVigo) then
		-- Vigo no longer a follower
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerVigo)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerVigo, false)
	
		-- Vigo Travel to Gate Unlock marker loc
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(followerVigo, locCSDGateUnlockVigo, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_RUN, true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerVigo, locCSDGateUnlockVigo)
		
		-- Vigo says "Stay Close"
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convVigoBark4, followerVigo)
	end
	
	-- Make sure both Neyrelle and Vigo's Q's are empty before swapping
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(followerVigo, convVigoBark4)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerVigo)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerNeyrelle)
	
	-- Swap Vigo and Neyrelle to Static
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerVigo) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(followerVigo)
		end
		
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(followerNeyrelle)
		end
	Hydra.ActorEnable(NeyrelleCSDGate)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(VigoCSDGateUnlock)
	
	-- Vigo Open door
	Hydra.QActorAnimLoop(VigoCSDGateUnlock, animUseLoop, 1)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(VigoCSDGateUnlock)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(idDungeonDoor)
end
